  "texts": [
    "This model can be used for a range of multi-scale and multi-purpose task predictions or optimization.",
    "One of the key predictions our model can make is the physical and biological doses of RPTs.",
    "By considering the properties of the radiopharmaceutical, and human body factors, our model could predict the delivered dose to both the tumor and normal tissues.",
    "These predictions can inform treatment planning and help ensure that the prescribed dose is appropriate and safe.",
    "Another prediction our model can make is the clinical outcome in terms of tumor response, disease progression, and survival."
